{"wiki_doc_id":"1134997640360193638","title":"不良人","subtitle":"画江湖之不良人中的门派","abstract":"不良人，是国产动画《画江湖之不良人》系列中的门派。原型为历史上的唐代官职不良人。唐代官府中的一个秘密部门，类似于明代锦衣卫，只对皇帝负责。有天罡三十六校尉。唐末，黄巢作乱，官军无力平叛。于是在京城陷落前夕，不良人携皇室至宝龙泉剑销声匿迹，再没有人知道他们的下落。不良帅袁天罡暗中将手下不良人遣散到各个藩镇势力中潜伏下来，静待时机以图东山再起。现在驻地为藏兵谷。","schema":"sslocal://microapp?app_id=tt11ae67138e958492\u0026bdp_log=%7B%22launch_from%22%3A%22general_search%22%2C%22search_id%22%3A%2220230511222746358452C688450E2E7DB8%22%7D\u0026scene=022002\u0026start_page=pages%2Fwiki_v2%2Findex%3Fdoc_id%3D1134997640360193638%26baike_source%3Ddouyin_search\u0026version=v2\u0026version_type=current\u0026bdpsum=99ff76f","head_image":"https://p1-bk.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-mlhdmxsy5m/ba65477e663842438059f4eb49ae651a~tplv-mlhdmxsy5m-cspd:256:256.image","display_type":"4","head_image_base64":"","schema_h5":"sslocal://webview?url=https%3A%2F%2Fm.baike.com%2Fwikiid%2F1134997640360193638%3Fbaike_source%3Ddouyin_search%26enter_from%3Dgeneral_search%26keyword%3D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2589%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%26search_id%3D20230511222746358452C688450E2E7DB8%26search_result_id%3D9216470812267422550%26is_douyin_baike%3D1%26status_bar_height%3DHEIGHT\u0026hide_nav_bar=1\u0026trans_status_bar=1\u0026should_full_screen=1\u0026hybrid_sdk_version=bullet\u0026loading_bgcolor=ffffff\u0026\u0026disableBounces=1\u0026use_bdx=1\u0026enable_bullet_trace=1\u0026sdk_type=baike\u0026enable_webview_select_search=1","pc_site_url":"https://www.baike.com/wikiid/1134997640360193638?baike_source=douyin_search\u0026enter_from=general_search\u0026query=%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E4%BA%BA\u0026search_id=20230511222746358452C688450E2E7DB8\u0026search_result_id=9216470812267422550\u0026is_douyin_baike=1\u0026result_type=baike_wiki_doc_general_search","quick_facts_list":["画江湖之不良人中的门派"],"recall_alias":"","catalog_list":[{"name":"门派介绍","schema_h5":"sslocal://webview?url=https%3A%2F%2Fm.baike.com%2Fwikiid%2F1134997640360193638%3Fbaike_source%3Ddouyin_search%26enter_from%3Dgeneral_search%26keyword%3D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E
